                <h1>How to Easily Remove Background Color in Word</h1>
                <p>To remove the background color in Microsoft Word, follow these simple steps. First, select the text or paragraph with the background color you wish to change. Next, navigate to the "Home" tab and click on the "Shading" dropdown in the Paragraph section. Choose "No Color" to eliminate the background. This will ensure your document looks clean and professional.</p>
